data.description: Click Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this exquisite home that sits on a culdesac, with no back neighbors and features, new flooring, new paint throughout and a recently updated bathrooms. The open floor plan welcomes you into a spacious living room  with a beautiful brick fireplace. The kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, a large island. Formal dining room is great for gatherings, with a built-in desk off the kitchen offers space to study or work. The primary bedroom is complete with an ensuite bath that includes dual sinks, a gorgeous shower, and a relaxing soaking tub. Step outside to a fully fenced backyard, covered patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining. The expansive green space and fire pit area create an inviting atmosphere for chilly nights. With walking trails, a community park and pool, and nearby shopping and restaurants at Grand Parkway Marketplace, this home offers an ideal lifestyle for both relaxation and recreation."
